description: Our favorite Eminence tells a story about the great string bassist George "Pops" Foster -- and dinner was delicious.  Recorded on August 30, 2019, at Dan's apartment, by Michael Steinman for JAZZ LIVES (http://www.jazzlives.wordpress.com).
